  • Constructor Details

    • FacilitiesInfo

      public FacilitiesInfo()
      Default constructor. Initializes the firebase instance and prepares an empty list of events. The facilityID is left unset.

    • FacilitiesInfo

      public FacilitiesInfo(String address, String facilityName, String owner, Double longitude, Double latitude, String facilityImage)
      Constructs a new FacilitiesInfo object with specified address, facility name, owner, longitude, and latitude. A unique facility ID is generated automatically.
      Parameters:
      address - The address of the facility.
      facilityName - The name of the facility.
      owner - The owner of the facility.
      longitude - The longitude coordinate of the facility's location.
      latitude - The latitude coordinate of the facility's location.

    • FacilitiesInfo

      public FacilitiesInfo(String address, String facilityName, String owner, String facilityImage)
      Constructs a new FacilitiesInfo object for test purposes
      Parameters:
      address - The address of the facility.
      facilityName - The name of the facility.
      owner - The owner of the facility.

  • Method Details

    • facility

      public HashMap<String,Object> facility()
      Returns a map representation of the facility's information. The map contains the facility's address, name, owner, and events.
      Returns:
      A hashmap containing the facility's data.
